'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 61''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 61''',  was the sixty-first issue of ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', published in [[December]] [[2005]] and covering [[January]] and [[February]] [[2006]]. It was 100 pages long.

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Com-Scan]]
*[[Best of Hyperspace]]: Lights, Camera, Jedi: The Sets of Episode III {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 84}}
*Collecting
*[[Set Piece|Technical Readout: Geonosis Arena]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 84}}
*[[Star Wars Q&A|Q&A]]
*[[Comlink (department)|Com-Link]]
*[[The Jawa Trader]]

===Features===
*"[[The Art of Revenge of the Sith]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 84|''Star Wars Insider'' 84]]}}
*"[[Multiple Personality]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 83|''Star Wars Insider'' 83]]}}
